  <brief_title>Evaluation of Predictive Visual Analog Scale (VAS) for Determining the Ingesta of Patients Carrying a Digestive Cancer</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Centre Hospitalier Universitaire de Nice</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Centre Hospitalier Universitaire de Nice</source>
  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of our study is to determine if the evaluation of ingesta of cancer
      patients by VAS (on the day of hospitalization) is able to predict the actual ingesta of
      patients during hospitalization (for patients malnourished, at risk of malnutrition or risk
      free).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
